# A procedure for obtaining [[amniotic fluid]] from the [[uterus]] of a pregnant woman, or the [[amniotic sac]] of other animals, by inserting a hollow needle through the [[abdominal]] wall.  Used in diagnosing possible [[genetic]] defects and/or [[obstetric]] complications.